						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1450 (1528 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription is highly damaged and illegible. It gives an elaborate list of provisions made for conducting a number of specified festivals. Of the details of the date all that could be made out is the <hi rend="bold">Śaka year 1450.</hi> It corresponds to <hi rend="bold">1528 A.D.</hi></p>						

